Adjusted the Transit Network Shape panel styling in `website/src/pages/index.module.css`.

Readability changes:
- darkened and simplified the panel background gradient
- raised text opacity to near-white
- increased monospace font size and weight
- added slight letter spacing and text shadow
- disabled ligatures for cleaner glyph rendering

These changes target the exact complaint: the monospace diagram content is now materially stronger against the background.
